      "post_content": "Time to put a dollar value on Powercreep in Magic!  \n  \n[Jace, The Mind Sculptor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jace, The Mind Sculptor) ($90)- [Brainstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm) ability ($0.90) - [Unsummon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unsummon) ($0.01) - Powercreep = [Precognition](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Precognition) ($0.30)  \n  \nRearranging our Equation and solving for $$$ yields:  \nPowercreep = $88.79",
